      "content": "that's a good start. it definitely hits the right notes. can you expand on the part about 'modern progressive agendas'? i want to name-check some of the specific things they're pushing that actually threaten the family unit, so people see exactly what the danger is. make it sound like these aren't just different opinions, but actual threats to our way of life.",
